Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白的  好漂亮  像雪一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不捡吗  那来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  给妈妈看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  男子汉不能动不动就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要独自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心  玩得开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为教学合宿要去雁羽温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  要让您出合宿的费用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到温泉附近的窑户去帮我取茶碗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来联络说是马上就能做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  滋叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得真吓人  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保镖跟去是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人所托去做事  当然是很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「强梁霸道终殄灭  恰似风前尘土扬」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  上午的课就上到这里  午饭前是自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  接下来去干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然先去泡温泉啦  温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我还有点重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在森林乱窜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物很碍眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚出森林  废物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你滚出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么  欺负这么小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类竟敢小看我们  不知天高地厚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一样爱管闲事啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次可算是白来了  还得再过来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛  茶碗要明天才能做好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是麻烦的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是放食物的容器  在附近的超市买就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说就太直截了当了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不是容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是容器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8\fad(0,300)}（注：猫咪老师把俗语作字面理解了,「没有身体和盖子」）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  要过去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  别睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我被丢向夏目的粉笔打中了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭会是什么呢  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目总是笑着  但总觉得不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言和姿势  连气息…也觉得不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许他并不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跟我一样化为人形独自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  跟我一起住在这森林就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头疼了  明天就要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于亲近的话他就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本没法去取茶碗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课前能不能赶回去都是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人  我也能帮助别人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我说「谢谢你了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是没用的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去摘蘑菇  摘很多很多  分给夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  小狐狸  你还赖在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不长记性的家伙  说了叫你滚的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这森林不需要你这种废物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不再是废物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不是…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的小子  不可原谅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说过叫你们住手的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用拳头还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘记了吗  夏目玲子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过到春天就将名字还给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的玲子  又干这种罪孽深重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天？这是第几个春天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  茶碗拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧 早蕨 这是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个友人帐的主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐？我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被写下名字的就会以主仆之契建立关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被夺走名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才归还了名字  怎么会去夺取名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我做你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会起到作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很软弱吗  我没用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想用这种东西来互相束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是主人跟手下的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们拥有其他的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友介绍给我一处好窑户
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为家族增加了  就借机订一套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的份  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小狐狸说的那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有没有用的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想给夏目也看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…我想见夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉不能动不动就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定要变强  总有一天能帮上夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想见夏目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听过传言了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像认识那个拥有友人帐的夏目嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能完全化作人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能让我吃鱼吃个饱  就告诉你能跟夏目见面的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…你能告诉我跟夏目见面的方法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨狐狸  你被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你这么笨  才会总是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目早就忘记你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能变成人类一天的药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成人类的药？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见面只要自己去见就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要去见他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我好歹也是狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去人类的世界  就能追寻夏目的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目一个人有没有寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  夏目的气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你没事吧  一个人吗  妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见他  好想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里  夏目在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦  快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是夏目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大丰收嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目的气味  在这里  就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了哦  贵志钓的真鳟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是条好真鳟  开动了  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志能吃河鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我都能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃的东西要说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋他不吃青椒  像小孩子一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我小时候也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  有同伴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子  这真鳟非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也尝一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好吃  能吃到这么美味的东西真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  夏目看起来很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的…寂寞的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那时的小狐狸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  特地来见我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得记住路啊  下次我去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算寂寞也不敢迈出脚步  没想过去做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以或许很多东西就无法察觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:51.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}虚幻之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人能看见妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与之交心  终于成为了重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得无法看见妖怪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个人能幸福  我就没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

